content.raw:
Do you by any chance have multiple instances of protobuf installed? I might try installing

```
sudo apt-get install -y libprotobuf-dev
```

but outside of that it could be a ton of things if you’ve used your native OS system before for development. I do have a working compilation of subt tunnel\_circuit on my native OS that I have recompiled this morning so I do know it can work.
